Actual Working Code For Nuit Blanche Project:
SymphonieLumineuse/sensorAndLightsLargeRange.py = Reading IR Sensor Value from 100-600 to create a diferent hue.  Needs to be smoothed and change so there is different colour schemes
SymphonieLumineuse/demo.py = Simple demo going through a Color Wheel. This part of the code (with parts added) will be used to every 15 minutes.


